data.description: Welcome to Weybridge community - located in the heart of Royal Palm Beach! Enjoy the amenities that this community has to offer - such as the clear pool to jump into during the hot summer months and the basketball court to enjoy a friendly competition amongst friends. In this quiet, all-age community, you will locate our new listing - a spacious townhome waiting for its new owners. This abode has over 1,700 square feet of living space, with a total of 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Enjoy the privacy that comes with this townhome, as you have your own fenced-in patio where you can enjoy BBQ nights with friends and family all year long! Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a property within this up and coming city!
